bination might be novel or non-existent, requiring proximate searches.\n\n    *   *Sub-questions:*\n        1. Existence of DVS-PEI adhesive coatings? (Weak/None)\n        2. Application on plasma-activated PP? (Weak/None)\n        3. Application on Al2O3? (Weak/None)\n        4. Measured peel/lap-shear strengths? (Weak/None)\n        5. MD predictions of single-bond work of adhesion? (Weak/None)\n        6. Comparison between experiment and MD? (Weak/None)\n\n    *   *Gaps:* All of them.\n\n    *   *Queries:* Need to be sharper.\n\n    *   *Okay, ready to generate.*\n","chars":8558,"prompt_excerpt":"You are a research search strategist conducting an agentic deep research loop.\n\nRESEARCH QUESTION: What experimental evidence exists for divinyl sulfone (DVS) crosslinked polyethylenimine\n  (PEI/BPEI) adhesive coatings on plasma-activated polypropylene and aluminum oxide\n  substrates, and how do measured peel or lap-shear adhesion strengths compare with molecular\n  dynamics predictions of single-bond work of adhesion?\n\nROUND HISTORY:\nRound 1: 9 queries -> 60 web + 0 academic, 56 new URLs, 3 page","input_tokens":1439,"output_tokens":3112,"reasoning_tokens":2165},{"ts":"2026-03-12T02:02:23.745903+00:00","vid":"WEB_20260312T015506_435334","node":"structured","type":"reasoning_capture","call_type":"structured:PageSummaryBatch","reasoning_text":"Thinking Process:\n\n1.  **Analyze the Request:**\n    *   **Role:** Research analyst reading web pages for a deep research project.\n    *   **Research Question:** What experimental evidence exists for divinyl sulfone (DVS) crosslinked polyethylenimine (PEI/BPEI) adhesive coatings on plasma-activated polypropylene and aluminum oxide substrates, and how do measured peel or lap-shear adhesion strengths compare with molecular dynamics predictions of single-bond work of adhesion?\n    *   **Input:** 4 pages of content (actually only 3 distinct pages provided in the prompt text, though the instruction says \"Read the following 4 